Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.30,0:01:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎少爷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.48,0:02:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二十话\N真古流的复活！\N呼风唤雨终极之杀人剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.13,0:02:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用这双眼睛看到了.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人被传说的理由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 这里都是急流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.10,0:03:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙已经回不来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.90,0:03:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.30,0:03:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑哥还没回来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.51,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候\N如果我跟剑心一起去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是剑哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.13,0:03:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.23,0:04:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.63,0:04:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小惠小姐…由太郎少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.07,0:04:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子 好烫喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.11,0:04:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掉到海里 溺水了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.71,0:04:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直昏迷不醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.88,0:04:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么湿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.39,0:04:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让各位担心真是对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.39,0:04:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连你都这样了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.53,0:04:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.30,0:04:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.60,0:04:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎和小薰小姐\N都由我来保护…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.91,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只会担心别人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.01,0:04:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了别人可以不要自己的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.71,0:04:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心真是笨蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快要跟政府战斗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.52,0:05:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个大房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.53,0:05:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将成为我们的城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底要开始什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人到底是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎少爷\N已经全部都交给雷十太大人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.61,0:05:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是少爷现在到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太罗嗦了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.45,0:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷现在很安全…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位先暂时离开这大房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村先生一定会救我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.06,0:06:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.27,0:06:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑术是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.53,0:06:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟被杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.54,0:06:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两者合而为一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始你是我们的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.35,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.91,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真古流的传说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在维新后不久已经在流传着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那时候起政府也注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是毫无道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.22,0:07:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀人剑登峰造极的剑客们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要建设国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.03,0:07:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能丢弃剑的武士的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以小生来说是可以理解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是总觉得要流很多血的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.94,0:07:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去说服一下的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.21,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.07,0:07:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经受伤了 你还在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 而且他们并不是说了\N就能明白的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.21,0:07:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.31,0:07:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的缺点是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.58,0:07:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.65,0:07:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人就能背负所有的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了有我存在这可不太好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.59,0:07:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.09,0:07:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.06,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什..什么嘛 不要笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.33,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位 这里的名产是温泉馒头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请吃看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馒头 我要吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.54,0:08:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,惠姐跟小绫小雀到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.24,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们出去采药草了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要一次就塞进嘴巴里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.32,0:08:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 你醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.22,0:08:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脸色已经好很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.76,0:08:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是你的家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是..是.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.30,0:08:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为某些原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望由太郎少爷暂时住在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.80,0:08:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.20,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是你救我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.87,0:08:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回到雷十太师父那里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.18,0:08:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你这不知好歹的混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.98,0:08:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.08,0:08:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想赶你出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.38,0:08:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是剑心说\N不要让你再回去雷十太的身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竹刀只是玩具而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.96,0:08:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师父说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.86,0:09:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有真的日本刀\N才能有优越的灵魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太..师父吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.77,0:09:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,师父是我的理想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.34,0:09:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走的话\N用那支日本刀把我打倒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来分胜负吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.59,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是真的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.99,0:09:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了也可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.31,0:09:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太教你的\N好像是输的那方面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.55,0:09:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…罗嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.72,0:10:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要偷逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.53,0:10:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要出去的话\N就堂堂正正的打败我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下..我还没输呢.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.04,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人从输中才会长大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.14,0:10:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输了也不是没有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.48,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.72,0:10:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没教过由太郎少爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.69,0:10:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道这个的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要练习看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.89,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷活心流的练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷…活心流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了你后就觉得技痒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.24,0:10:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能引以为荣真正的剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.91,0:10:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以从心理开始陷进去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.67,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个练习…可以成为强者吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.88,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会成为强者的…一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 帮我练习吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.42,0:11:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三天以内我一定要胜了那家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.19,0:11:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.62,0:11:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是泡澡的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.03,0:11:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定不逃走要打倒你为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.53,0:11:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后再正大光明的\N从这个家里走出去给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始练习攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.98,0:11:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种动作很简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.85,0:11:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 完全不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.69,0:11:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 哪里不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷活心流是保护人的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.70,0:11:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护…人的剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 只要有保护心爱人的心\N就会成为力量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心爱的人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.54,0:11:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用有杀气的力气去挥刀是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.52,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.76,0:12:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.83,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变强者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对   就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.47,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很认真的在练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.68,0:12:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是很认真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常有剑才的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的呼吸不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.10,0:12:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.63,0:13:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙比想像中的还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.18,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神谷活心流…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.71,0:13:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么的.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.98,0:13:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉这么的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以上是我们的计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.90,0:14:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最强的男人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.74,0:14:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是把失去的荣誉\N找回来的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.87,0:14:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有剑 我们才不会灭亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.71,0:14:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起来吧 各位精锐们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.18,0:14:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为野望的国家来战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.79,0:14:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.38,0:14:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是我钓的比较大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太哥的最大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.99,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.66,0:15:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常的热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.39,0:15:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我的大房子不太一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶而这样也许不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太哥 鱼烤好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.87,0:15:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.00,0:15:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有下毒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.68,0:15:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己钓的鱼\N烤起来吃这是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.85,0:15:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劈柴也是 擦地也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到吃东西\N这么没品格的人也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！真是讨厌的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.03,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心..我有一件事非常在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在要说出来了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.60,0:15:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有剑心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没有现在的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.51,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.24,0:15:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也没办法跟小薰小姐练习了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.08,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.15,0:16:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.28,0:16:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把剑心的勇气用在剑上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.29,0:16:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是剑心比雷十太还要好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.12,0:16:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又另当别论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.96,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师父很相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以让我加入真古流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要成为强者\N以报答他的恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 把竹刀拿来就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.74,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要向祢彦再挑战一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.94,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去拿吧 由太哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.22,0:16:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦 你不来监视我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.69,0:16:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.49,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 也许我会逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是破坏约定的那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.06,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在打倒我之前\N不会从这里逃走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.60,0:16:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.87,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不错的孩子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.51,0:16:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是非常棒的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.07,0:17:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从心里祈祷雷十太能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.41,0:17:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点   快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.18,0:17:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！有客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.95,0:17:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是警察署长村木
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.79,0:17:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说绯村先生在这里\N所以从东京来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.36,0:17:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的话 现在在河边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.59,0:17:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我住在附近 叫冢山由太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冢山？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.77,0:17:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你是\N现在纠纷中的大房子的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了避开骚动 而在这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.91,0:17:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.27,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的房子发生了什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？陆军…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像注意到我们的动静了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.62,0:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人看到\N枪声部队陆续的集中来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 比想像中的还要早
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如我所期望的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去迎击他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.83,0:17:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打败那枪声部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.37,0:18:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙知道 老练的剑术
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.60,0:18:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是最强的杀人兵器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.28,0:18:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我的王国 开始的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陆军特种部队要攻击真古流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.02,0:18:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是连新闻\N都不能泄漏的国家机密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.09,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道\N政府在注意真古流的动向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.19,0:18:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里是把他们\N全部消灭的最佳时机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.06,0:18:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山县大人也是相同的想法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.66,0:18:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是听到绯村大人\N与真古流有接触后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要我来听听你的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我来的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在如果用力量\N来刺激那些家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必定会造成无谓的流血事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.95,0:18:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.28,0:18:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎不见了 哪都找不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.99,0:18:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟由太郎说了什么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不..并没有全部都跟他说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.69,0:18:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？剑心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.73,0:19:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想他已经回到大房子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.31,0:19:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府的命令\N从这里开始不能通行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.38,0:19:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冢山的房子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.75,0:19:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.58,0:19:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长！附近的居民\N已经都让他们去避难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.07,0:19:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师父！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.99,0:20:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击 射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.88,0:20:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道真古流的力量吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.99,0:20:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑的力量…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕！准备射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.89,0:20:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪是没有什么用处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.36,0:20:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我这支刀的面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.47,0:20:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由太郎 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要阻止战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下去 改变从外面的攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.16,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受伤的人抬出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.33,0:21:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请求支援部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.90,0:21:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…请告诉我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.77,0:21:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷十太师父…
